description: Back on market due to buyer financing falling through! DON'T MISS OUT AGAIN! Discover this beautifully maintained South Boston gem, featuring two bedrooms and one bathroom. This move-in ready home offers a spacious kitchen with modern stainless-steel appliances. The sunny and generous living room, highlighted by a charming bow window, creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. Additional perks include convenient laundry and private storage space in the basement. The bedrooms work perfectly for roommates or couples looking for a home office. In this desirable East Side location, you will enjoy easy access to public transportation with several bus routes (#11, #9, and #7) just steps away. A short stroll brings you to Carson beach, and nearby shops and restaurants on East Broadway enhance the appeal of this prime location. This property represents a fantastic opportunity for both first-time homebuyers and investors. Don’t let it pass you by!
